GLOBAL_LATENCY_DESCRIPTION: change GLOBAL_LATENCY to your lowest usual ping
RACE_MARRIED_DESCRIPTION: Kick 1 is faster on Aman Male, Baraka, Castanic F, Human F, Popo. Set to true if you are those races.
AUTOFAQFIRE_DESCRIPTION: Auto Faq fire after Radiant/Penetrating/TB - REQUIRES ROBOTJS
FAQFIREKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Sequential Fire, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
INCIN_RESTRAIN_DESCRIPTION: Auto Restraining after ranged Incindary Arrow. - REQUIRES ROBOTJS
RESTRAINKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Restraining Arrow, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
AUTOWOLLEY_DESCRIPTION: Instantly volley when locked on - REQUIRES ROBOTJS
WOLLEYKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Arrow Volley, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
DISABLE_CHANGE_DESCRIPTION: this will disable charge bar emulation, useful for people who have unstable net and prone to get stuck or server lagging badly
DISABLE_CHANGE_DESCRIPTION_2: disabling charge actually does not significantly impact ping tax, because charge skills are actually not ping taxed if you simply release the skill early
SPOOF_SKELETON_DESCRIPTION: greatly speeds up charging skills, however may cause asynchronization with high jitter
RF_PRESET_STOP_DESCRIPTION: stops RF from casting if it presets when you just hold down the key.
AUTOFAQFIRE_GHOST_DESCRIPTION: Auto FAQ fire after Ghost arrow - REQUIRES ROBOTJS
AUTOR_WW_DESCRIPTION: Auto Windwalk after Rapidfire last hit - REQUIRES ROBOTJS
WWKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for WindWalk, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
AUTORF_WW_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Auto Windwalk after Rapidfire last hit delay in milliseconds. Scales with ASPD.
